The high technology innovation corporation shall be exempt from the following state laws:
     (1)  Section 78-1, relating to public employment;
     (2)  Chapter 36, relating to the management of state funds;
     (3)  Chapter 38, relating to deposits of public funds; and
     (4)  Chapter 76, relating to civil service. [L 2005, c 173, pt of §1; am L 2006, c 282, §4]
